OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782910143
OL,3,CHalifax brand scrapped after 173 years
OL,4,Cas customers moved to Lloyds
OL,6,FThe 173-year-old Halifax brand is
OL,7,Fbeing scrapped and all customer
OL,8,Faccounts will be changed to Lloyds
OL,9,Fover time, the building society's
OL,10,Fowner has said.
OL,12,FLloyds Banking Group, which has owned
OL,13,FHalifax since 2009, said there is
OL,14,Fnothing that customers need to do and
OL,15,Fthey will be contacted about the
OL,16,Fchanges.
OL,18,FThe banking giant confirmed the move
OL,19,Fafter reports in May said it was
OL,20,Fconsidering phasing out Halifax as a
OL,21,Fstandalone brand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
