FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782910143
OL,3,CHalifax brand scrapped after 173 years
OL,4,Cas customers moved to Lloyds
OL,6,FIt is understood that the decision was
OL,7,Frooted in efforts to simplify the
OL,8,Fgroup's portfolio, with the
OL,9,Fdistinction between Halifax and Lloyds
OL,10,Fseen as becoming less prominent in
OL,11,Frecent years.
OL,13,FHalifax was founded in West Yorkshire
OL,14,Fin 1853 and granted its first
OL,15,Fmortgage, before growing to become one
OL,16,Fof the UK's largest building societies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
