OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782910143
OL,3,CHalifax brand scrapped after 173 years
OL,4,Cas customers moved to Lloyds
OL,6,FJas Singh, Lloyds Banking Group's
OL,7,Fchief executive of consumer
OL,8,Frelationships, said: "As Halifax
OL,9,Fchanges to Lloyds, our Halifax
OL,10,Fcustomers will keep everything they
OL,11,Fknow and love today ` the same
OL,12,Ffantastic app design, the same
OL,13,Ffriendly faces in our branches ` even
OL,14,Fthe same sort code and account number.
OL,16,F"But as Lloyds customers, they'll get
OL,17,Fthe best innovation and experiences we
OL,18,Foffer."
OL,26,@pD@VOUxD@AOUzD@GO]
