OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782910143
OL,3,CHalifax brand scrapped after 173 years
OL,4,Cas customers moved to Lloyds
OL,6,FLloyds said it remained committed to
OL,7,Fthe town of Halifax and the wider
OL,8,FYorkshire and Humber region, where
OL,9,Fsome 3,000 staff are based at its
OL,10,FTrinity Road office.
OL,12,FNo job cuts are being announced as
OL,13,Fpart of the shake-up, and Halifax
OL,14,Fbranches will either be rebranded to
OL,15,FLloyds or shifted to a Lloyds branch
OL,16,Fnearby throughout 2027.
